 Director and the Chairman Emeritus of C J  Thomas Company  Inc  In 1986  he founded Rural Housing Reinsurance Company  Ltd of Hamilton  Bermuda  and serves as that company s president  Mr Miller graduated from VMI with a degree in History and served two years in the U S  Army as a Cavalry officer  Mr  Miller is a member of the VMI Foundation s Board of Trustees  joining the Board in 2009  This is his second term as a trustee  he previously served from 1991 to 1999  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 